2008-08-13 14:43  olivier.salaun

	* src/tools.pl, web_tt2/error.tt2, web_tt2/help_admin.tt2,
	  web_tt2/manage_template.tt2, web_tt2/modindex.tt2,
	  web_tt2/review.tt2, web_tt2/viewmod.tt2, wwsympa/Challenge.pm,
	  wwsympa/SympaSession.pm, wwsympa/cookielib.pm,
	  wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [feature] Added a new function for the
	  moderation of messages. On rejection of messages personalised
	  messages can be created and saved and used to give more
	  information as to why these messages were refused by the
	  moderator.
	  (change] Extended web session management to store 'cas-server',
	  'sso-id', 'do_not_use_cas' and 'checked_csa' data in the session
	  table instead of HTTP cookies (as it used to do). Also changed
	  the SympaSession methods to have separate store() and renew()
	  methods.

