2008-07-31 15:33  olivier.salaun

	* soap/sympasoap.pm, src/Commands.pm, src/List.pm, src/mail.pm,
	  src/report.pm, src/sympa.pl, src/task_manager.pl:
	  [feature][#3984][requested by S.Kristoffersen, Univ. Oslo] Sympa
	  is now setting the Auto-Submitted SMTP header field for messages
	  it generates. It also prevents loops for incoming message that
	  have this header field set.
	  See related draft
	  http://www.tools.ietf.org/html/draft-palme-autosub-01

2008-07-04 12:04  olivier.salaun

	* src/mail.pm: [-feature] Added initial comments from Soji Ikeda
	  explaining the concerns about charset management.

2008-06-17 09:37  sympa-authors

	* mail_tt2/listmaster_notification.tt2, src/List.pm,
	  web_tt2/create_list_request.tt2, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [feature]
	  notify list creation and list copy to listmasters with
	  one_time_ticket
	  [-bug] Fix notification of copy list

2008-06-16 13:36  serge.aumont

	* src/Conf.pm, src/Scenario.pm: [feature] New sympa;conf parameters
	  log_module and log_condition. log_module is used to activate logs
	  for a specific module.
	  Current version provide only logs for scenario . log_condition is
	  used to controle in which case logs are applied. Both are
	  multivaluated (list of values comma separated).
	  exemple :
	  log_module scenario,smtp
	  
	  log_condition ip=127.0.0.1,email=foo@domain
	  
	  log_module is not implemented for most modules. 'log_module smtp'
	  should replace the option sympa.pl -m

2008-06-16 10:21  david.verdin

	* src/List.pm: [bug]When storing subscription requests, Sympa
	  ignored subscription request if an user had already asked for a
	  subscription, event if the new request was for another list.
	  Fixed by checking the list name before searching previous
	  subscription requests for the user.

2008-06-12 15:42  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [bug][#3917] Changing language after a
	  search in the archives results in an
	  error. Now redirecting to 'arc' function instead

