2008-05-29 13:03  david.verdin

	* wwsympa/wwslib.pm: [bug] Passwords were lower-cased by default
	  when compared to the password stored in the database. This was
	  completely incompatible with the new password storage as a MD5
	  hash. Fixed by removing this lower-casing.

