2008-05-23 16:08  olivier.salaun

	* soap/SympaTransport.pm, soap/sympa_soap_client.pl,
	  soap/sympasoap.pm, wwsympa/SympaSession.pm, wwsympa/cookielib.pm:
	  [change] Changes regarding SOAP session management :
	  * SOAP session now uses the session DB table
	  * session_id can be validated, checked, used in
	  authenticateAndRun()
	  * sympa_soap_client.pl has been extended : new --session_id
	  option, new supported service --service=getUserEmailByCookie

