2008-04-01 09:52  david.verdin

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [Reported by J.M. Beuken, univ. cat.
	  Louvain] Fix: When copying a template through the web interface,
	  HTML was not unescaped before writing the file. c onsequently,
	  the file used to reload the page for template edition had escaped
	  HTML. for critical files such as main.tt2 or title.tt2, this
	  caused the web page diaply to choke on tt2 parse errors.

