	  administration button in the admin page.

2008-03-25 10:12  david.verdin

	* wwsympa/bounced.pl: Fix: When a bounce file could not be created,
	  nothing was done, so at the next bounced.pl iteration, the faulty
	  report was still present. In such a case, the bounce report is
	  now moved to bad.

