2008-03-11 16:04  david.verdin

	* po/Makefile: Change: Now, when performing "make update-po", the
	  catalogue file to update is temporarily saved to avoid losing
	  strings from beta version when updating stable version, or
	  vice-versa. Both updated and saved files are then merged.

