	* web_tt2/ticket.tt2: New template

2008-02-29 11:05  david.verdin

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [#3790][Reported by R. Tassoni, National
	  Library of Australia and T. Danel] Fix: When displaying a message
	  to moderate in the web interface, if a document was attached to
	  the message, the link to display the message lead to empty
	  documents.
	  This was because we didn't take into account the fact that
	  MHonArc put the file in a subdirectory.
	  Fixed by changing the kind of ergument file passed from scalar to
	  vector.

2008-02-29 10:37  serge.aumont

