2007-08-31 16:23  david.verdin

	* src/tools.pl: Change: new try to improve XSS control. Now, in
	  areas where HTML is not allowed, the parameters is tested against
	  W3C compliant tags and attributes, or attributes containing
	  javascript.

2007-08-30 13:00  david.verdin

	* src/tools.pl: Change: refined Simple XSS filter. Don't ding on
	  simple "<" only, but on <script, <meta and <fdfds javascript:

