2007-08-21 14:44  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [M.Massar, univ Kaiserslautern] New
	  feature: Sympa is now able to get the Email in SubjAltName. As I
	  was not able to fi
	  nd the mentioned patch to mod_ssl to get SSL_CLIENT_S_EMAIL
	  exported, I wrote another patch based on SSL_CLIENT_CERT fr
	  om "SSLOptions +ExportCertData". REAPPLY the patch that had been
	  removed.

