	* src/Upgrade.pm: Added $charset to do_log()

2007-08-21 12:20  david.verdin

	* .version: 5.4a3 (first test with sessionning)

2007-08-20 13:19  serge.aumont

	* src/Conf.pm, src/Language.pm, src/List.pm, src/Log.pm,
	  src/Upgrade.pm,
	  src/etc/global_task_models/purge_session_table.daily.task,
	  src/etc/script/create_db.Oracle, src/etc/script/create_db.Pg,
	  src/etc/script/create_db.SQLite, src/etc/script/create_db.Sybase,
	  src/etc/script/create_db.mysql, src/task_manager.pl,
	  src/tools.pl, web_tt2/dumpvars.tt2, web_tt2/javascript.tt2,
	  web_tt2/login_menu.tt2, web_tt2/main.tt2,
	  web_tt2/serveradmin.tt2, web_tt2/show_sessions.tt2,
	  wwsympa/Makefile, wwsympa/SympaSession.pm, wwsympa/cookielib.pm,
	  wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Introduction of http session in ordre to
	  replace a lot of cookies, for better user interface and security.
	  -new table session_table
	  -new module SympaSession.pm
	  -new features
	  - from admin page set log level for the current session
	  - from admin page list active sessions
	  - from admin page change user email identity
	  -new task to purge old sessions from table (inactive delay to
	  remove session is set by the sympa.conf parameter
	  session_expiration_period (defaul 1 month)
	  -session start at first hit usually with an anonymous user. The
	  session continue when the user logging.
	  -cookie lang replaced by a session parameter
	  -cookie sympa-user removed
	  
	  TODO : introduce user pref based obn session for review page
	  length and archive thread/chrono view . Need to introduce a
	  structure data varchar column in user_table
	  
	  

2007-08-20 08:29  olivier.salaun

	* soap/sympasoap.pm: [reported by O.Berger, INT] Fix: typo in
	  List::store_susbscription_request() would make
	  sympa_soap_server.fcgi die while receiving a subscription request
	  with moderated subscription.
	  The "use strict" pragma has been added and many other typos have
	  been fixed.

2007-08-17 14:56  olivier.salaun

	* src/Upgrade.pm: [reported by C.Peck, William and Mary
	  university]Fix: Upgrade process could make subscribers
	  unsubscribeable. The subscribed_subscriber DB field was first set
	  to 1 but then turned into 0 (because of an old enum2int problem).
	  Changed the order of the upgrade processes.

2007-08-10 15:04  olivier.salaun

	* src/Conf.pm: Change: css_url default value is now
	  static_content/css/current_robot. This make it possible to set a
	  single Apache Alias directive for static_content, shared by all
	  virtual hosts.

2007-08-10 13:41  olivier.salaun

	* src/Conf.pm: [A.Hicks, Persistent Objects] Fix: css_url and
	  css_path are not being set from the main config if they do not
	  exist in the robot config as they are being set before the
	  static_content_* checks

