	* src/sympa.pl: [suggested by T.Berry, NASA] Changed the process
	  identifier in the logs from (message) to (distribute)

2007-08-07 15:28  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Fix: no more use the buggy regexp
	  $tools::regexp{'html-free'}. It would regexp any string
	  containing '60' or '3c'

2007-08-07 13:52  david.verdin

	* po/check_locales.pl, src/Language.pm: [reported by JG.Pailloncy,
	  O.Girard and JMM. da Cruz] Fix: setlocale() failed on FreeBSD
	  because locales syntax were not standard (ll_CC.ISO8859-N instead
	  of ll_CC.ISO-8859-N). Now using utf-8 as encoding, thus solving
	  the problem. Also changed the algorithm used by check_locales.pl
	  to be the same as Language::SetLang()

2007-08-07 11:52  olivier.salaun

	* src/Scenario.pm: Fix: remove trace

2007-08-07 11:49  olivier.salaun

	* ChangeLog: Update

2007-08-07 11:48  olivier.salaun

	* src/Scenario.pm, src/tools.pl: Fix: (related to latest scenario
	  changes) [listname] variable could not be evaluated while
	  verifying a scenario rule

2007-08-07 09:17  olivier.salaun

	* ChangeLog: Update

2007-08-07 09:14  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/bounced.pl: Fix: missing trailing ';'

2007-08-07 09:13  olivier.salaun

	* src/task_manager.pl: Fix: missing trailing ';'

2007-08-07 08:55  olivier.salaun

	* .version, ChangeLog, NEWS: Preparing 5.4a.2

2007-08-07 08:38  olivier.salaun

	* src/Scenario.pm: Fix: scenario cache was not used

2007-08-07 07:39  olivier.salaun

	* soap/sympasoap.pm, src/Commands.pm, src/List.pm, src/Makefile,
	  src/Scenario.pm, src/sympa.pl, web_tt2/d_control.tt2,
	  web_tt2/edit_list_request.tt2, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Change: new
	  Scenario.pm module. The way autorization are loaded has changed :
	  they are now stored in a central place, ie a single copy of a
	  scenario is stored if 2 lists use it. This should make the sympa
	  processes consume less memory when running lots of lists. The
	  scenario are now reloaded whenever they change on disk, except
	  for operations that require good performances (like the 'lists'
	  command). Inclusion of third party scenarios is now performed at
	  evaluation time (in request_action()) and not while loading the
	  scenario as it used to be.

2007-08-03 12:29  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Change: give up the pre-load of lists using
	  get_lists()

2007-08-03 12:15  olivier.salaun

	* src/List.pm, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Change: added a new Robot
	  package inside List.pm. Also optimized List::get_lists() to cache
	  the results within a session and prevent multiple browsing of the
	  expl/ directory

2007-08-03 08:23  olivier.salaun

	* src/List.pm: Change: removed some obsolete code since
	  user_data_source now has a single value

2007-08-03 08:00  olivier.salaun

	* soap/sympasoap.pm, src/Commands.pm, src/Family.pm, src/List.pm,
	  src/task_manager.pl, wwsympa/bounced.pl, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi:
	  Change: removed obsolete List::save() subroutine and calls to it

2007-08-03 07:48  olivier.salaun

	* NEWS, src/List.pm, src/Upgrade.pm, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Change:
	  merging any value of user_data_source to 'include2'. This change
	  should help simplifying and optimizing the code. Later the
	  user_data_source parameter could be removed.

2007-08-01 15:48  olivier.salaun

	* .version, ChangeLog, NEWS: preparing 5.4a.1

2007-08-01 13:51  olivier.salaun

	* src/List.pm: Change: optimizations to lower the List::new() calls
	  and perform locks on list config files only if reloading is
	  required

2007-08-01 12:30  olivier.salaun

	* src/Log.pm, subst.pl: Change: optimizations to save most calls to
	  do_log()

2007-08-01 11:16  olivier.salaun

	* src/task_manager.pl: Change: check the $end variable before
	  processing each task, thus making a kill -TERM more quickly
	  processed

