	  the "magic authentication" with the SSO service name, defined in
	  auth.conf

2007-05-25 11:39  david.verdin

	* src/Upgrade.pm: probe_db() now updates primary key only if it is
	  not fair to its definition in Sympa. This prevents us from
	  removing and recreating perfectly compliant primary keys anytime
	  the function is called.

