	* .version, src/Upgrade.pm: Change : During upgrade process, if an
	  existing primary key is incomplete, it is completed.

2007-05-09 15:12  david.verdin

	* src/Upgrade.pm: Fix: Found new index names to remove from
	  previous installs.

2007-05-09 13:20  olivier.salaun

