2007-02-19 10:28  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Fix: arcsearch would crash wwsympa process
	  if provided a search expression with both invalid expression and
	  \n, because tools::escape_regexp() does not apply on multi-line.
	  Changed the allowed regexp for wwsympa incoming parameters to
	  forbid \n in most of them.

