	  decode string with wide characters".
	  Now opening archives as bytes (not utf8) to prevent decoding

2007-01-30 16:34  olivier.salaun

	* src/tools.pl: Fix: don't redirect stderr to a file if process
	  runs in foreground.
	  Also changed the owner of the ;stderr file

2007-01-30 16:16  olivier.salaun

	* wwsympa/Marc/Search.pm: Fix: arcsearch_id would fail on some
	  messages.
	  Marc::Search expectes mhonarc to add X-Subject data to generated
	  HTML files. Some examples were found with X-Subject value split
	  among 2 lines.
	  Marc::Search::search() is now able to parse split X-Subject
	  entries.

2007-01-29 16:37  olivier.salaun

	* src/mail.pm: Change order

2007-01-29 09:15  olivier.salaun

	* mail_tt2/listmaster_notification.tt2, src/sympa.pl,
	  src/task_manager.pl, src/tools.pl, wwsympa/archived.pl,
	  wwsympa/bounced.pl: New feature: STDERR of daemons is redirected
	  to a file. If process crashes,
	  next process started will detect the failure and send a notice to
	  listmaster.

