2006-10-18 10:07  sympa-authors

	* check_perl_modules.pl, src/Commands.pm, src/Language.pm,
	  src/List.pm, src/Message.pm, src/mail.pm, src/tools.pl,
	  src/tt2.pl: [Soji Ikeda] Changes: Sympa now uses new Perl modules
	  MIME::Charset and
	  MIME::EncWords to encode characters. These modules are
	  alternatives for
	  MIME::Words with better handling of multibyte charsets.

