2006-08-25 15:26  sympa-authors

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [reported by S.Amrani, Gendarmerie Nat.]
	  Fix: After editing a subscriber email, the list owner might get a
	  "not subscribed to list" error.
	  The bug happened because the do_set() is used by both list
	  members and list owners. Wwsympa now used the previous_action
	  information to bring the user back to the right page.

