	  wwsympa/wwslib.pm, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [Adrien Brard] New
	  feature: DB logs
	  Each operations theat changes the status of
	  messages/subscriptions/list config is now logged in a structured
	  DB entry. Both listmasters and listowners can search this events
	  DB using the Sympa web interface.

