	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: Fix: raise an error if no msgid is provided
	  to do_send_me()

2006-06-07 14:15  sympa-authors

	* check_perl_modules.pl, doc/sympa.tex.tpl, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi:
	  [M.Massar, univ Kaiserslautern] New feature: Sympa is now able to
	  get the Email in SubjAltName.
	  As I was not able to find the mentioned patch to mod_ssl to get
	  SSL_CLIENT_S_EMAIL exported, I wrote another patch based on
	  SSL_CLIENT_CERT from "SSLOptions +ExportCertData"

