	* ChangeLog: Preparing a 5.3a.3 before adding trombi feature

2006-06-06 13:51  sympa-authors

	* src/Language.pm: [reported by P.Maes, Univ. Louvain] Fix:
	  localization failed on Solaris. The native Solaris gettext
	  libraries failed to use the appropriate .mo file.
	  We're now using the "Pure Perl" implementation of gettext

2006-06-06 09:06  sympa-authors

	* src/Conf.pm, src/List.pm: [reported by P.Maes, Univ. Louvain]
	  Don't use chown user.group that fails on Solaris. Run separate
	  chown and chgrp commands instead

