	* src/etc/mhonarc-ressources.tt2: [proposed by E.Hood] Fix: now
	  using $FROMADDRNAME$@$FROMADDRDOMAIN$ instead of $FROMADDR$. See
	  https://savannah.nongnu.org/bugs/index.php?func=detailitem&item_id=11759

