	* src/Language.pm: [reported by P.Maes, Univ. Louvain] Fix: locales
	  would not work with Solaris. Solaris requires that
	  POSIX::setlocale() is run before Locale::Messages::textdomain()
	  and Messages::bindtextdomain()

