	* src/List.pm: [BugID 664] [E.Rynes, Case Western Reserve
	  University] Fix: The get_first_admin_user subroutine in Lists.pm
	  does not free up the DB statement handle on a failed lookup. This
	  causes
	  the database (at least when using oracle) to run out of cursors
	  when the number of lists is high.

