	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [bugID 567] Change: if 'web_recode_to' is
	  set, decode incoming parameters from this charset to perl's
	  internal encoding (utf-8). This is required for CJK binary
	  strings that can't be used in perl regexp.

