	  doc/html/sympa.ps, doc/sympa.ps, doc/sympa.tex,
	  doc/sympa.tex.tpl, src/Conf.pm, src/List.pm,
	  src/etc/script/Makefile, src/etc/script/create_db.SQLite,
	  src/sympa_wizard.pl: [Id 446] New feature: Added support for an
	  SQlite backend.A create_db.SQLite has been added. Sympa.pl is
	  able to automatically create the database if none exists. SQLite
	  is now the default 'db_type' in sympa.conf (SQlite drivers
	  include the database engine itself, therefore nothing needs to be
	  installed).

