	  web_tt2/review_family.tt2, web_tt2/serveradmin.tt2,
	  wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [G. Bouteille] New feature: 1st version of
	  list families. List families make it possible to automatically
	  create a set of mailing lists that share a common configuration
	  template,
	  a set of constraints, templates and authZ scenarios. Family
	  instantiation requires an XML document that defines mailing
	  lists.

