	  wwsympa/archived.pl: Change: archives were not properly TT2
	  parsed. Content of mhonarc-ressources uses different TT2 tags (
	  (-% and %-) ). Inclusion of files with absolute/relative path
	  should not be allowed for security reasons. Email addresses in
	  message body and also spam-protected now.

