2003-11-25 13:39  salaun

	* src/List.pm: [reported by P.Maes] Fix: on Solaris shared lock
	  fails with "Bad file number" error. This is due to the fact that
	  flock() perl functions uses lockf() system call that requires the
	  locked file to be open in read mode.

2003-11-24 09:36  salaun

