	  by pamelant AT nerim.net] Change: Postgresql 7.3 has no support
	  for not SQL standard type 'datetime'.
	  ***** If you are upgrading from a previous Sympa version, you
	  should update
	  ***** your sympa DB as follows :
	  ***** ALTER TABLE subscriber_table CHANGE date_subscriber
	  timestamp with time zone NOT NULL;
	  ***** ALTER TABLE subscriber_table CHANGE update_subscriber
	  timestamp with time zone;

