	* src/List.pm, src/tools.pl: [reported by G. Paressant] Bug fix: if
	  email entries returned by List::_include_users_ldap() contained
	  spaces characters,
	  then the database update could lead to a "duplicate entry error",
	  causing the List::sync_include() to fail

