	  where found
	  in SQL or LDAP query result

2002-10-24 12:59  salaun

	* src/sympa_wizard.pl: [BugID 58] [reported by Xavier AT
	  cs.gouv.qc.ca] Fix: sympa_wizard used temporary files in /tmp/ ;
	  if /tmp/ was
	  an a different filesystem than /etc/, then the rename() would
	  fail. No more use temporary files.
	  Change: only warn if rename() of previous cong files failed

