2002-10-10 16:04  salaun

	* wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [BugID 52] Fix : Moderated messages were
	  not accessible from the web interface.
	  WWSympa runs as user 'sympa' and the mhonarc process that
	  generates HTML version
	  of moderated messages also requires to run as user 'sympa'.
	  Obviously Perl
	  refused to allow this script to run as SetUID 'sympa' because
	  mhonarc had
	  double quotes (") in its argument.

