2001-09-19 10:18  salaun

	* Makefile, src/List.pm,
	  wwsympa/wws_templates/fr/edit_list_request.fr.tpl,
	  wwsympa/wws_templates/us/edit_list_request.us.tpl,
	  wwsympa/wwslib.pm, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [Florent Guilleux] New
	  feature: Task manager
	  wwsympa/wws_templates/fr/edit_list_request.fr.tpl
	  Various task automatic processing. List master may use predefined
	  task models to automate recurrent processings such as regurlaly
	  reminding subscribers their belonging to a list or updating
	  certificate
	  revocation lists. It is also possible to write one's own task
	  models to
	  meet particular needs. Unique actions may also be scheduled by
	  this way.

