2001-02-28 10:21  salaun

	* src/Commands.pm, src/List.pm, src/smtp.pm, src/sympa.pl,
	  src/tools.pl: Bug fix : Sympa would break S/MIME signatures if
	  message contained encoded parts.
	  This is due to MIME::Entity library use. It would not always
	  encode the msg
	  exactly the original way (Ex : number of columns for Base64) ;
	  S/MIME signature
	  is broken.
	  Correction : Unless message body was altered (header/footer
	  added), Sympa
	  uses the original message's body, bypassing MIME::Parser

2001-02-28 09:41  salaun

