2001-02-09 15:46  salaun

	* KNOWNBUGS: Bug fix

2001-02-09 15:11  salaun

	* src/List.pm: [reported by Ronan Salmon] bug fix :
	  Can't call method "compute_auth" on unblessed reference

2001-02-09 11:24  salaun

	* doc/sympa.tex, nls/fr.msg, nls/us.msg, src/Commands.pm,
	  src/List.pm, wwsympa/wwsympa.fcgi: [Olivier LACROIX] New list
	  parameter 'available_user_options'
	  Only available reception modes are listed on the web interface.
	  If a user sets a forbidden mode (not listed), he is asigned the
	  mode
	  in 'default_user_options'.
	  If default_user_option reception mode is not listed in
	  'available_user_options'
	  it is appended to it.

